Program: Last Word
Title: 18/09/2009
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00mlxfp
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Sep 2009
Matthew Bannister presents the obituary series. BBC Foreign Correspondent Brian Barron - correspondents Martin Bell and Michael Nicholson, and cameraman Eric Thirer pay tribute; Keith Floyd - Rick Stein and TV producer David Pritchard remember the TV chef; memories of agricultural scientist Norman Borlaug from his friend Dr Ed Runge; and Alan Alda and Stephen Armstrong remember comedy writer Larry Gelbart. Show less